00:07:59.590 --> 00:08:01.790
to get lost if they
don't understand

00:08:01.790 --> 00:08:03.680
what matters for them.

00:08:03.680 --> 00:08:07.480
So it is very important for
you to organize the LiveOps

00:08:07.480 --> 00:08:10.300
events to avoid your
users getting swamped

00:08:10.300 --> 00:08:12.700
by the flood of LiveOps.

00:08:12.700 --> 00:08:14.410
So from the next
