influencer video on YouTube.

00:12:40.600 --> 00:12:42.700
And then every TV
commercial wants

00:12:42.700 --> 00:12:46.850
aired to promote this
LiveOps campaign after that.

00:12:46.850 --> 00:12:49.270
I know it sounds like
a lot of investment,

00:12:49.270 --> 00:12:52.500
but for Mixi, actually it
was a really natural thing,

